  "prompt": "Where can I find device art generators for Samsung S5?",
  "response": "As of my last update, finding specific device art generators for older models like the Samsung Galaxy S5 might be a bit challenging since most resources are focused on newer models. However, you can still use general device art generators that allow you to upload custom templates or select from a variety of device frames. Here are some options and tips:\n\n1. **Online Device Mockup Generators**:\n   - **Smartmockups** (smartmockups.com): This service allows you to upload your own device templates and create mockups. You can find or create a Samsung S5 template to use here.\n   - **Placeit** (placeit.net): While it may not have specific options for the S5, it offers a wide range of device mockups where you can upload your designs.\n   - **Mockup World** (mockupworld.co): Offers free mockups templates, including smartphones, where you can find or adapt an S5 mockup.\n\n2. **Design Software**:\n   - **Photoshop & Illustrator**: If you have access to Adobe\u2019s software, you can create custom device art using a Samsung S5 template. You can find templates online from various graphic design resources.\n   - **GIMP**: As a free alternative to Photoshop, GIMP can also be used with the appropriate templates.\n\n3. **Community Forums & Resources**:\n   - **XDA Developers** (forum.xda-developers.com): This community might have resources or links to device art generators and templates for the Samsung S5.\n   - **Reddit**: Subreddits like r/androidthemes might have users who can direct you to resources for creating device art for older models.\n\n4. **Mobile App SDKs**:\n   - **Android Studio**: For developers, Android Studio provides tools to create device frames (including for older devices) to showcase apps and designs.\n\n5. **Direct Search for Templates**:\n   - **Google Search**: Try searching for \"Samsung Galaxy S5 mockup template\" or \"Samsung Galaxy S5 device art generator\". You might find specific resources or templates that you can use in various design tools.\n\nRemember, when searching for specific templates or art generators for an older device like the Samsung Galaxy S5, flexibility and a bit of DIY adaptation might be necessary. Using the available templates in combination with your design skills or the tools provided by the above services should allow you to create the device art you're looking for.",
